---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const pageTitle = "Work";
const description = "Resumé of Michael P. LeRoux";
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle} description={description}>
  <section class="mb-20">
    <h1>{pageTitle}</h1>

    <p class="mb-10">
      I'm currently available for contract or permanent work in the Boston area.
      I'd <a href="mailto:&#109;&#105;&#099;&#104;&#097;&#101;&#108;&#046;&#108;&#101;&#114;&#111;&#117;&#120;&#064;&#103;&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#046;&#099;&#111;&#109;" target="_blank">love to talk</a> if you think
      my experience would be a good fit.
    </p>
    <hr class="mb-10" />

    <h2 class="mb-2">Michael P. LeRoux</h2>

    <p class="mb-0">
      Somerville, MA • <a
        href="mailto:&#109;&#105;&#099;&#104;&#097;&#101;&#108;&#046;&#108;&#101;&#114;&#111;&#117;&#120;&#064;&#103;&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#046;&#099;&#111;&#109;"
        aria-label="Email"
        target="_blank">Email</a
      >
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      LinkedIn: <a
        href="https://linkedin.com/in/michaelleroux"
        aria-label="LinkedIn"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        target="_blank">linkedin.com/in/michaelleroux</a
      > • GitHub: <a
        href="https://github.com/mpleroux"
        aria-label="GitHub"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        target="_blank"
        >github.com/mpleroux
      </a>
    </p>

    <h3 class="pt-3">SUMMARY</h3>

    <p>
      Web Developer with full stack experience and a focus on building polished,
      consistent user interfaces. Dedicated to maintainable code, clear
      documentation, and a culture of collaboration and mentorship. Currently
      building on a professional background in Vue.js and the broader web stack
      to expand my toolkit with React, Next.js, Astro, and AI-assisted tools
      like Claude Code.
    </p>

    <h3 class="pt-3">TECHNICAL SKILLS</h3>

    <ul>
      <li>
        <b>Core Proficiencies:</b> JavaScript (ES6+), TypeScript, Vue.js, Nuxt, Tailwind
        CSS, Python, Django
      </li>
      <li>
        <b>Tools & Platforms:</b> Git/GitHub, AWS, Storyblok CMS, REST API Integration
      </li>
      <li>
        <b>Development Standards:</b> Agile/Scrum, Responsive Design, Web Accessibility
        (a11y), Technical Documentation, Component-Driven Architecture, Design Systems
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="pt-3">INDEPENDENT STUDY</h3>

    <ul>
      <li>
        Actively building personal web development projects using React,
        Next.js, Astro, and Claude Code
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="pt-3">PROFESSIONAL EXPERIENCE</h3>

    <h4 class="mb-0">
      Senior Software Engineer &ndash; EnergySage &ndash; Boston, MA
    </h4>
    <p class="mb-1"><i>October 2012 &ndash; June 2025</i></p>

    <ul>
      <li>
        Created scalable Vue.js components using TypeScript and an internal
        design system, improving UI consistency and developer efficiency.
      </li>
      <li>
        Integrated Storyblok CMS to empower non-technical stakeholders to
        independently update content, reducing engineering support requests.
      </li>
      <li>
        Standardized styling across multiple codebases, reducing UI drift and
        simplifying maintenance.
      </li>
      <li>
        Developed and maintained solar marketplace and clean energy content
        platforms across a full stack including HTML, CSS, JavaScript,
        Bootstrap, Python, and Django.
      </li>
      <li>
        Authored technical documentation for architectural decisions and
        frontend services to streamline onboarding and cross-team knowledge
        sharing.
      </li>
      <li>
        Mentored junior developers through code reviews and pair programming,
        accelerating their growth into independent contributors.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h4 class="mb-0">Web Developer &ndash; Verndale &ndash; Boston, MA</h4>
    <p class="mb-1"><i>April 2012 &ndash; October 2012</i></p>

    <ul>
      <li>
        Developed responsive, accessible website templates from design specs.
      </li>
      <li>
        Collaborated with QA to ensure cross-browser compatibility and reliable
        user experiences.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="pt-3">EDUCATION</h3>

    <h4>
      B.S., Computer Science &ndash; University of Massachusetts Dartmouth
    </h4>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
